string-array.name: wisdom
string-array.item: Don\'t spend a $1.00\'s worth of time on a $.10 decision.
Time flies. It\'s up to you to be the navigator.
Time is life. To waste your time is to waste your life.
No man was ever wise by chance.
How we spend our days is, of course, how we spend our lives.
There is no right way to do the wrong thing.
Do today what must be done. Your tomorrow may never come.
Time lost is never found again.
You can\'t catch one hog when you\'re chasing two.
All the flowers of all of the tomorrows are in the seeds of today.
If it weren\'t for the last minute, a lot of things wouldn\'t get done.
Work expands so as to fill the time available for its completion.
The bad news is time flies. The good news is you\'re the pilot.
Those who make the worst of their time most complain about its shortness.
We say we waste time, but that is impossible. We waste ourselves.
Regret for wasted time is more wasted time.
As if you could kill time without injuring eternity!
The years teach much which the days never know.
Time is an illusion. Lunchtime doubly so.
Grow old along with me! The best is yet to be.
I\'ve been on a calendar, but never on time.
Time spent with cats is never wasted.
Time is the only comforter for the loss of a mother.
To live is so startling it leaves little time for anything else.
Time makes more converts than reason.
An unexamined life is not worth living.
He not busy being born is busy dying.
The mass of men lead lives of quiet desperation.
Whatever you are, be a good one.
